text: Sangaris obtusicarinata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dmytro Zajciw in 1962. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Sangaris obtusicarinata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1962
title: Sangaris obtusicarinata
